reviews.review_text: Their doctors and staffs are very helpful and professional. The doctor prescribed me to do the ultrasound receptionist gave me the instruction how to book easily and faster. Once they received my report they called me and arranged me to see the doctor. Also they are so friendly and nice.

This clinic is conveniently located, just a few steps away from where we get off. The doctors are highly professional, quickly identifying the cause of the illness and providing appropriate treatment. They explained the diagnosis report in great detail. The receptionist at the front desk is polite and patient, helping us make appointments efficiently.

Doctors and staffs are extremely helpful and professional. The receptionists are always amazing. I m not familiar with their online booking system, they took their time, patiently and show me how to book it step by step. Doctors answer all my questions without rushing me out, and the wait wasn t too long. I always leave impressed.

J-Von Medical Clinic impressed me with their prompt response and efficient service. Upon receiving the lab results from my x-ray test, they quickly scheduled a follow-up doctor appointment. I really appreciate their extra care for me. Their commitment to promptness and attentive service is commendable.
My kid cried a lot due to flu shots. But the doctor and nurses are very patient and tried to comfort my kid. Also dr Chen sent my kid a sticker after the shot
Doctors are very nice and professional. My doc discovered my condition in time and treated me as quickly as possible.

The medical s online booking system is super convenient, and I no longer need to call in for booking appointments. This user-friendly feature has made managing healthcare appointments a breeze. I highly recommend it!

I received a follow-up call from the front desk to schedule a review of my lab reports, immediately after my results became available online. I am truly grateful for Dr. Zong and his exceptional front desk team, who have made me feel well-cared for
Friendly efficient receptionists, the doctors are patient and resourceful. Highly recommended.

I ve been here a number of times for various issues   the doctors are great, and the appointments do not feel rushed. The girls at the front do a great job given the very high volume. While in the waiting room I ve overhead them dealing with some very rude patients (I bet they don t act the same way when their coffee takes too long at Starbucks). I hope those patients realize there are systemic issues in the province and a shortage of GPs as there is not enough financial incentive to become a GP. The result is doctors and clinics being stretched thin and is no fault of the clinic itself.

Took my son there for his check-up recently, and he was super anxious about it. I thought he would freak out like when we were at his fluoride treatment, but surprisingly he was really into talking with the receptionists at the front. The ladies were super considerate and cheering to my son. They also gave him some stickers when we walked in, I thought that was really nice! Thank you ladies for making our visit easy and smooth!

Orignally, I gave give Five stars to Dr. Gill for his patience, persistence and general helpful, caring attitude. I still recommend him as a doctor, but my frustration is with his Front Counter Receptionists as I had a missed call from J-Von Medical, but a patient cannot return a call or email them (I tried several times, unsuccessfully)!  In the past, Ive been able to book online and speak with Dr. GILL. However, even though I am an Existing patient, the on-line system wont accept my email (same one I have had for 20 years!) I had to contact Vancouver General Hospital to try and get a message to my Doctor...who I have not heard back from in weeks! I was sent the email by the Doctor to get in touch with this medical clinic, yet it is the very same email that I have received messages  directly from J-Von Medical that states: Do Not email to this address as messages will Not be answered!

I ve been in this clinic with Dr. Zong , for few years, it s been a good experience with Dr and receptionists , I know they are very very  busy and they have to deal with so many things specialist people with bad manners, I was there once with my new born baby a guy was screaming at them and he didn t even was a patient of this clinic he was a husband of a patient, which I felt very sorry for the ladies at front desk . I wish they can extend their phone line so we can call anytime at the day as before .
Dr. Liu is super nice and professional. The receptionists are also efficient and helping.

Excellent doctors at this clinic. Dr. Zong goes above and beyond for his patients! The medical office assistants recently gave me a call to book for check up in person appointment was very efficient. With added booking online for virtual appointments made it easier for me have more regular doctor check ups as I am not required to wait long walk in times. And when I did have to go into the clinic I felt exceptional safe with all the Covid protocol the office had. Only complain I had was that during my short visit there, some possible wait in patients did try to barge in while being very rude to the office assistants. Its not something that clinic have control over, but during pandemic time, its truly sad that people are not more understanding of protocols.

i ve been a patient at jvon for a few years and this is a great clinic with great doctors. the doctors here have always helped assess my medical issues. the front desk are always helpful and patient whenever i have additional questions

I saw Dr. Nguyen here for probably 2.5 years. The staff was always very helpful and polite. I made online appointments and never waited more than 4 minutes - there was generally good availability to book appointments. Ive just transferred to someone much closer to my house and everyone helped so much to make that a smooth transition.
I had a bad experience with Customer Service and Doctors; If you want to waste time and be treated like nobody else go visit them and in the end you will be frustrated
They helped me make a CT appointment and called me to remind. So nice

Once you walk in, you know you are in good hands. Although many people on here complain about the receptionists (yes, I think they need some more training in telephone communication, manners, courtesy, etiquette, etc.), I do think that this clinic is super efficient in my personal experience. Let me give you a few examples: 1) While the clinic my cousin goes to regularly refused to refer him  to a gastroenterologist, J-Von did it timely and soon he had the endoscopy and colonoscopy done; 2) While the clinic my cousin goes to never called him after receiving the endoscopy and colonoscopy results, J-Von called as soon as they received the fax and booked him immediately for a follow-up to give him peace of mind; 3) After J-Von prescribed my mother a new drug, J-Von called us a few days later for a follow-up. Besides, Dr. Zong, a young doctor, has up-to-date knowledge and is English-Mandarin bilingual. I want to ask you: How many clinics would go that far to do these? None! If you had an unpleasant experience here and if it is all trivia (like with the receptionists, etc.), come on, have some patience and give it more time! It cant be wrong.

I had my first appointment today,  Joyce did teeth cleaning for me.  She is very patient and detail-oriented,  did an awesome job. Howard Liu is also very friendly and helpful, without being pushy about making my next appointment.  They even tried to ask my previous dental office for my x-ray so that they can save money for me!  Awesome experience!
thank you jvon for your best service! The front staff explained my dad the requisition which he really appreciates it! He cannot English so he let me say something. Best clinic ever

First off, I have to say I dont usually rate medical/dental clinics. After all, I dont go around town trying different clinics. If I dont like one, I just dont go there anymore. And if I find one thats satisfactory, I will stay there. Im guessing most people are like me. And once in a while (if youre lucky) you will come across a clinic that goes above and beyond your expected level of service and knowledgeable staff. Such is the case with J-VON Medical and Dental. They have set a new standard of what customer service should be. They also have a very well trained team of medical experts and dental professionals. The first time I walked in I was greeted with a friendly smile by the super helpful reception team. They were able to book an appointment time that worked for me, given my busy schedule. And when I came in for my appointment they recognized me and greeted me by my name. How awesome is that? It really felt like a warm personal welcome. The clinics are always clean, and the place looks so modern. All the equipment there looks new and the technology used in some of these are pretty slick. The dentist who was assigned to me was named Howard. I cant say enough of his professionalism and respect. He works with his patients to ensure they have all the information to make the best decision with regards to the treatment plan or procedure. I highly recommend this medical/dental clinic because of the friendly knowledgeable staff, exceptional service, and highly trained professionals. And on top of that, they are so conveniently located next to Metrotown Station and super clean and modern.

I have been seeing Dr. Zhai for several times this year. She understood me very well. She is very professional,  responsible , and patient.  After getting the reports, she also gave me suggestions about diet and life styles. She is very helpful. I really appreciate her.

I am a Chinese and I speak Cantonese. My family doctor is Dr Cheung. When I need an appointment, their staff always try to help me getting an appointment. I am a patient with multiple medical conditions; they will call me if my tests are abnormal and follow up with me. staff are super friendly. They also offer virtual appointment with Dr. during COVID pandemic. They are helpful and professional, Great clinic!
Doctor is so patiently. The place is very convenient for me.
Dr. Qiming Wu is one if the best family Doctor. He is very knowledgeable and very patient, my parents are lucky to meet him.

Very nice staffs and excellent precaution for COVID.  I feel very safe when I visit here each time. Dr Zhai is amazing. She is so professional, empathtic and just a warm person. She listens actively. She gives a sufficient amount of relative information that I need and always offers options for me to choose, which makes me feel my rights and choices are respected. I feel very comfortable working with Dr. Zhai, Yun Lei, highly recommended! staff and excellent

I am now fully understand how much work theyve been putting in their jobs.  It is a very good clinic and people who came to their clinic so far, have a pleasure time with staff.  :) Thank You

Candy Cheung is a very good doctor. She is straight forward telling you what is your problem even you may not like to hear, but this is what a good doctor should do. We need someone like her to tell us the truth about our health. Thank you Doctor Candy Cheung.
I couldn t get a X-ray appointment time asap, so I called them for help. They were so nice to get an appointment for me. I appreciated that

I came this place for Family doctor and dental cleaning. Cindy is my family doctor and she was really patient to all my questions and gave useful suggestions. Joyce did a really good job on my dental cleaning and they waived my cleaning expense since I did the x-ray. They even gave me a liquid flosser for new patient gift. The most impressive thing for the dental clinic is, they mount a TV on the ceiling to allow patients watch TV while lying on the bed.
I am lucky to get a spot in and now they donot accept walk in anymore. The service is good, and doctors are amazing. Staff is fantastic.
Even though my appointment was really delayed. I was initially really upset but I appreciate that they were understanding and empathetic and reached out to apologize. They seem genuine to me!
